quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  64,1,jo cheez asmano mein hai aur jo cheez zameen mein hai ( sab ) khuda ki tasbeeh karti hai. isi ki sachhi badshahi hai aur isi ki tareef ( la-mutnahi ) hai aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  64,2,wohi to hai jis ne tum ko pedakiya phir koi tum mein kafir hai aur koi momin. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko daikhta hai
  64,3,isi ne asmano aur zameen ko mabni bar hikmat pedakiya aur isi ne tumhari soorten banayen aur soorten bhi pakeeza banayen. aur isi ki taraf ( tumhe ) lout kar jana hai
  64,4,jo kuch asmano aur zameen mein hai woh sab jaanta hai aur jo kuch tum chhupa kar karte ho aur jo khullam khula karte ho is se bhi aagah hai. aur khuda dil ke bheidoon se waaqif hai
  64,5,kiya tum ko un logon ke haal ki khabar nahi pohanchi jo pehlay kafir hue they to unhon ne apne kamon ki saza ka maza chakh liya aur ( abhi ) dukh dainay wala azaab ( aur ) hona hai
  64,6,yeh is liye ke un ke paas paighambar khuli nishanain le kar aeye to yeh kehte kekiya aadmi hamaray haadi bantay hain? to unhon ne ( un ko ) nah maana aur munh phair liya aur khuda ne bhi be parwai ki. aur khuda be parwa ( aur ) sazawar hamd (o sana ) hai
  64,7,jo log kafir hain un ka aitqaad hai ke woh ( dobarah ) hargiz nahi uthaye jayen ge. keh do ke haan haan mere perwar-digaar ki qasam tum zaroor uthaye jao ge phir jo kaam tum karte rahay ho woh tumhe betaye jayen ge aur yeh ( baat ) khuda ko aasaan hai
  64,8,to khuda par aur is ke rasool par aur noor ( quran ) par jo hum ne nazil farmaya hai imaan lao. aur khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai
  64,9,jis din woh tum ko akatha honay ( yani qayamat ) ke din akatha kere ga woh nuqsaan uthany ka din hai. aur jo shakhs khuda par imaan laaye aur naik amal kere woh is se is ki buraiyan daur kardey ga aur baghaye bahisht mein jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain daakhil kere ga. hamesha un mein rahen ge. yeh barri kamyabi hai
